Sentencas: La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-yttria-stabilized zirconia (LSCO-YSZ) composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) has been fabricated by wet impregnation method.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: Nitrate precursors of La, Sr, and Co have been impregnated into the pre-sintered porous YSZ matrix, which is converted into LSCO phase after calcination at 850 degrees C in the presence of glycine as confirmed from X-ray diffraction.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: LSCO of 5, 7, and 10 wt% impregnated porous YSZ have been electrochemically characterized using 2-probe AC conductivity method.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: Maximum ionic conductivity of 0.27 S/cm at 800 degrees C and activation energy of 0.15 eV between 600 and 800 degrees C have been observed for 10 wt% LSCO-YSZ cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: Area-specific resistance of 1.01 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C is estimated for the electrolyte-supported half-cell (10 wt% LSCO-YSZ/YSZ).
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: After testing the LSCO-YSZ cathode matrix, the electrolyte-supported full cell (10 wt% LSCO-YSZ/YSZ/NiO-YSZ) has been tested and produced maximum power density 51.12 mW/cm(2) (109.38 mA/cm(2)) at 800 degrees
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode
Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: The electrolyte-supported full cell exhibited 6 Omega cm(2) electrode polarization at 800 degrees C in H-2, which is in higher side leading to low performance.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode

Sentencas: LSCO-YSZ/YSZ/NiO-YSZ SOFC found to give stable performance up to 2 h and scanning electron microscopy analysis has been carried out before and after cell testing to assess the morphological changes.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical performance of La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 impregnated porous YSZ cathode
